<p class="lead">Start thinking. Ask questions to get your group thinking.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Pastor Robert called giving the ‚Äúverb of the Bible.‚Äù What‚Äôs the action word of your life?</li>
  <li>What do you think are the differences between the prosperity, poverty, and provision ‚Äúgospels‚Äù?</li>
