<p class="lead">Start praying. Be bold, and pray specifically.</p>

<ul>
  <li>God, thank You for giving me life, not once, but twice. Will You now give me the courage to spend my life giving back to You? Please help me to grow a heart of generosity toward my neighbors, my church, my family, and ultimately, You.</li>
</ul>

